Hey I decided to make a list of a bunch of famous people who graduated from George Washington University over the years. (included are links to sites with more information about these people.)

[Jacqueline “Jackie” Lee Bouvier Kennedy Onassis](Jacqueline Kennedy Onassis - Wikipedia) The widow of John F. Kennedy

[Harry Reid](http://reid.senate.gov/) United States Senator from Nevada

[John Foster Dulles](John Foster Dulles - Major, United States Army United States Senator - Secretary of State) Former Secretary of State

[David Fishman](http://www.castlewave.com/bio-david-fishman.htm) Co-founder of many high end technology companies
